               stealing, on the <rs id="t18290219-44-cd235" type="crimeDate">6th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290219-44-off234 t18290219-44-cd235"></join>, 2 pairs of window-sashes, value 2l., and 2 locks, value 4s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18290219-44-victim459" type="victimName">
                           Anthony 
                           Pratt
                        <interp inst="t18290219-44-victim459" type="surname" value="Pratt"></interp>
